resources.information_higherdisksize: Based on your estimate, we recommend that you provision a higher disk size.
resources.diskbursting_tooltiptext: Monthly charges for Disk Bursting are based on a transaction fee for IOPS processed beyond the provisioned amount, plus an enablement fee. Estimate your monthly charge using the maximum number of IOPS you expect to process, the duration (in minutes) at which you expect to process them in each working day, and the number of working days you expect to burst.
resources.information_atburstinglimit: Your expected max IOPS is at the bursting limit. We recommend that you provision a higher disk size if you intend to exceed this.
